Priestess Sophia: I believe I'm getting a little carried

Clea: You've offered yourself up again, haven't you? Next,

Thief Nora: Captain, you haven't been in any dangerous

Captain Clevo: That's right, but... you can't be serious!?

Cors the Wanderer: I already contacted you about the danger

Cors the Wanderer: It's because the master of this place,
